{"tid":680681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"90後青年情關闖不過　牛頭角上邨墮樓亡","createTime":"2018-05-27T11:02:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T13:02:05.000Z","uid":118120,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9e44449e9b5886dd38e4364605e7cc1cf573dfba","tid":680681,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T11:02:47.000Z","msg":"牛頭角上邨常逸樓男子墮樓身亡。今晨1時許，警方接報指一名姓郭（24歲）男子墮樓，倒臥大廈對開，保安員驚聞巨響發現報警。救護員證實已當場死亡，警方封鎖現場調查，並用帳篷遮蓋屍體，現場地上遺下一隻鞋。 <br />\n<br />\n警方在現場未有檢獲遺書，警員向大廈保安員了解，據悉，事發前，郭自行按密碼進入大廈，其後登上天台墮樓；警員經初步調查，事件並無可疑，死因有待剖屍確定。據了解，郭因感情問題不開心。 <br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線： <br />\n<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222 <br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000 <br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288 <br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255 <br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000 <br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281 <br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180527/mobile/bkn-20180527013427786-0527_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180527%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180527013427786-0527_00822_001.html&d=JLNiTcM%2FumB9ObWVpLrhmv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=52aff4ea\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180527/mobile/bkn-20180527013427786-0527_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/27/N9FP8d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2FN9FP8d.png&h=d417fe2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a27c4c2836dcfb27b0b2bfe3ec7b71e8eea172c","tid":680681,"uid":16961,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T11:03:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">難得一身好本領〜情關始終闖不過〜〜</span>"},{"pid":"f0ca3671d39d75447887e10eabae8d5cc8542e86","tid":680681,"uid":88887,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T11:03:53.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"9e6f7ab06785484269775bfc755e993f81672ce7","tid":680681,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T11:04:16.00